<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Security Notice</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: #0c0a1e;
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 520px;
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 48px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    .icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #f2efff;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    p {
      color: #9a92bd;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 32px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5865f2, #9b5cff);
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      transform: scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(88,101,242,0.4);
    }
    .btn:active {
      transform: scale(0.97);
    }
    .note {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    }
    .note a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="icon">🛡️</div>
    <h1>Developer Tools Detected</h1>
    <p>
      For security reasons, protected resources are not available while
      browser developer tools are open.
    </p>
    <p>
      Please <strong>close developer tools</strong> (F12 / Inspect Element)
      and then click the button below to continue.
    </p>
    <a href="/" class="btn">Return to site</a>
    <div class="note">
      <a href="/security-notice">Refresh this page</a> &middot;
      <span>If you are not using developer tools, this may be a false positive.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>